{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·006.1", "text_original": "厭浥行露，豈不夙夜，謂行多露。", "text_normalized": "厭浥行露，豈不夙夜，謂行多露。", "notes": "行露 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·006.2", "text_original": "誰謂雀無角？何以穿我屋？誰謂女無家？何以速我獄？雖速我獄，室家不足。", "text_normalized": "誰謂雀無角？何以穿我屋？誰謂女無家？何以速我獄？雖速我獄，室家不足。", "notes": "行露 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·006.3", "text_original": "誰謂鼠無牙？何以穿我墉？誰謂女無家？何以速我訟？雖速我訟，亦不女從。", "text_normalized": "誰謂鼠無牙？何以穿我墉？誰謂女無家？何以速我訟？雖速我訟，亦不女從。", "notes": "行露 Chinese stanza 3."}
